# Organisation Control Director Term Set Indicator

## identifier
de13729

## type
boolean

## definition
This indicates whether the board has set a particular length for a director's term.

## guidance
A choice of TRUE/FALSE values. 
true = the board has set a length for a director's term.
false = the board has not set a length for a director's term.

## syntax
### xbrl
- name=OrganisationControl.DirectorTermSet.Indicator
- classification=py/pyde/pyde.02.18
- period=instant
